01:16:15,395 --> 01:16:16,649
Porco gave him the loop.

1128
01:16:16,781 --> 01:16:17,828
Whats the loop?

1129
01:16:18,282 --> 01:16:21,161
The loop is what made Porco the Ace of the Adriatic!

1130
01:16:26,332 --> 01:16:27,333
He's got me!

1131
01:16:33,506 --> 01:16:34,507
He's gonna shoot!

1132
01:16:39,313 --> 01:16:40,241
