1149
01:17:12,017 --> 01:17:13,545
Cmon shoot!

1150
01:17:14,649 --> 01:17:15,691
Ah!

1151
01:17:15,711 --> 01:17:16,753
I bet your gun is jammed!

1152
01:17:16,773 --> 01:17:17,815
Isn't?

1153
01:17:17,835 --> 01:17:18,877
Serves you right pig!

1154
01:17:24,557 --> 01:17:25,900
They are coming towards us!

1155
01:17:28,863 --> 01:17:30,117
