1160
01:17:41,245 --> 01:17:42,107
Jump!

1161
01:17:42,127 --> 01:17:42,989
Jump!

1162
01:17:53,554 --> 01:17:54,160
Hey!

1163
01:17:54,180 --> 01:17:54,786
