1173
01:18:30,257 --> 01:18:32,114
Boy!

1174
01:18:32,134 --> 01:18:33,991
I really don't wanna miss this fight!

1175
01:18:35,137 --> 01:18:36,707
Is she coming on not?

1176
01:18:46,434 --> 01:18:48,941
Gina, Italians know about the fighting.

