01:18:48,961 --> 01:18:51,468
Get the pig out of there!

1178
01:18:51,574 --> 01:18:52,813
Ferrarin.

1179
01:18:57,076 --> 01:18:57,602
Marco!

1180
01:18:57,622 --> 01:18:58,148
I hope I'm not too late!

1181
01:19:17,127 --> 01:19:20,506
I cant believe that can keep this up.

1182
01:19:20,673 --> 01:19:22,801
Looks like the pig's fading.

1183
01:19:24,635 --> 01:19:26,979
Go on, Porco hang in there!

1184
01:19:31,308 --> 01:19:32,981
You must quit!

1185
01:19:38,524 --> 01:19:41,152
I'm not handing Fio over to a jerk like you!

1186
01:19:46,699 --> 01:19:49,043
He's got Curtiss's edge in sight!

1187
01:19:49,285 --> 01:19:50,707
It's over!

1188
01:19:55,220 --> 01:19:56,481
No!

1189
01:19:56,501 --> 01:19:57,762
No!

1190
01:19:57,782 --> 01:19:59,043
Don't jam now!

1191
01:20:02,840 --> 01:20:04,057
Gotcha!

1192
01:20:07,219 --> 01:20:08,892
What?

1193
01:20:09,471 --> 01:20:10,893
It can't be jammed!

1194
01:20:11,942 --> 01:20:13,487
It's not jammed.

1195
01:20:13,507 --> 01:20:15,052
You used up all your ammo, you idiot!

1196
01:20:15,696 --> 01:20:17,303
That's not good!

1197
01:20:17,323 --> 01:20:18,930
And no sucking gun and thanks to Fio's big butt!

1198
01:20:21,358 --> 01:20:24,407
I refuse to end this fight with a draw!

1199
01:20:26,206 --> 01:20:27,796
You stupid cowboy!

1200
01:20:27,816 --> 01:20:29,406
