1203
01:20:37,285 --> 01:20:39,251
Cmon give me a break.

1204
01:20:47,384 --> 01:20:49,102
You think that's funny?

1205
01:20:51,774 --> 01:20:52,775
you're not even cutting close!

1206
01:20:52,795 --> 01:20:53,796
Throw somethin' already!

1207
01:20:54,224 --> 01:20:55,341
You throw like a girl!

1208
01:20:55,459 --> 01:20:56,560
You don't even know anything about girls!

1209
01:20:58,103 --> 01:20:59,150
Shut up, pig!

1210
01:21:00,356 --> 01:21:02,108
What's goin' on up there?

1211
01:21:02,232 --> 01:21:03,484
Cmon Porco!

1212
01:21:12,451 --> 01:21:13,452
They're coming in!

1213
01:21:13,712 --> 01:21:14,667
Wait!

1214
01:21:14,687 --> 01:21:15,642
You're a bet!

1215
01:21:15,662 --> 01:21:16,617
The bets can't run off, Fio.

1216
01:21:17,132 --> 01:21:18,598
I go where the money goes!

1217
01:21:18,618 --> 01:21:20,084
Wait for me!

1218
01:21:26,256 --> 01:21:27,633
Why you crazy pig!

1219
01:21:29,676 --> 01:21:31,474
Come and get it cowboy!

1220
01:21:37,393 --> 01:21:38,770
Cmon put 'em up.

1221
01:21:39,103 --> 01:21:40,980
Fight with me, you weakling!

1222
01:21:48,095 --> 01:21:49,447
No, Porco!

1223
01:21:51,834 --> 01:21:55,913
Get up, Pig You cheating!

1224
01:21:55,933 --> 01:22:00,012
Shut up!

1225
01:22:23,490 --> 01:22:24,994
Cmon Porco, Block.

1226
01:22:25,014 --> 01:22:26,518
Uppercut!

1227
01:22:26,702 --> 01:22:27,130
Yeah!

1228
01:22:27,150 --> 01:22:27,578
Yeah!

1229
01:22:27,598 --> 01:22:28,026
Hit 'em.

1230
01:22:28,620 --> 01:22:30,018
Yes!

1231
01:22:30,038 --> 01:22:31,436
Now we got a boxing match.

1232
01:22:31,456 --> 01:22:32,854
The bets are still open!

1233
01:22:33,000 --> 01:22:33,594
Taking bets!

1234
01:22:33,614 --> 01:22:34,208
Taking bets!

1235
01:22:34,228 --> 01:22:34,822
Bring a bell up here!

1236
01:22:37,887 --> 01:22:40,000
Can't you fly this plane any faster?

1237
01:22:40,164 --> 01:22:42,337
Sorry maam, but I'm afraid the engine will overheat.

1238
01:22:43,125 --> 01:22:45,548
Seaplane pilots are all idiots!

1239
01:22:51,727 --> 01:22:53,442
Het Fio!

1240
01:22:53,462 --> 01:22:55,177
Did you see that left hook I threw?

1241
01:22:58,683 --> 01:23:02,232
I'm gonna finish you off in the next round.

1242
01:23:02,811 --> 01:23:04,279
This time I'm send you to dreamland Curtiss.

1243
01:23:04,386 --> 01:23:05,628
Hit him!

1244
01:23:05,648 --> 01:23:06,890
Hit him!

1245
01:23:07,316 --> 01:23:09,410
I'll wade a pushway you!

1246
01:23:11,487 --> 01:23:13,239
Come on, big womanizer!

1247
01:23:14,198 --> 01:23:16,371
You're the one who is a womanizer!

1248
01:23:18,202 --> 01:23:20,079
You fall in love with every woman you meet!

1249
01:23:20,204 --> 01:23:21,581
Your the one hoggin' in all the girls...

1250
01:23:21,997 --> 01:23:24,420
