1260
01:24:10,988 --> 01:24:11,891
That's a knockout!

1261
01:24:11,911 --> 01:24:12,814
Stop!

1262
01:24:12,995 --> 01:24:14,595
Round is out!

1263
01:24:14,615 --> 01:24:16,215
Back to your corner.

1264
01:24:19,471 --> 01:24:21,849
There they are!The Air Force hasn't arrived yet.

1265
01:24:26,870 --> 01:24:36,489
End of round 6 Round 7  Gina does not want me, liar.

1266
01:24:40,294 --> 01:24:41,548
I'm not lying.

1267
01:24:41,568 --> 01:24:42,822
