01:25:30,052 --> 01:25:31,534
I don't wanna see breaking anymore hearts!

1279
01:25:31,554 --> 01:25:33,036
You hear me?

1280
01:25:39,589 --> 01:25:40,895
9..

1281
01:25:40,915 --> 01:25:42,221
Yeee!

1282
01:25:42,241 --> 01:25:43,547
Porco!

1283
01:25:46,224 --> 01:25:47,271
The winner!

1284
01:25:47,392 --> 01:25:49,190
Porco, Thank you!

1285
01:25:49,353 --> 01:25:51,902
Yeah, piece of cake.

1286
01:25:59,081 --> 01:26:00,984
Okay, listen up everybody.

1287
01:26:01,004 --> 01:26:02,907
The Italian Air Force is on its way here.

1288
01:26:03,533 --> 01:26:06,810
