1289
01:26:06,979 --> 01:26:08,434
Come to the my place.

1290
01:26:08,454 --> 01:26:09,909
Drinks are on the house!

1291
01:26:11,360 --> 01:26:12,461
Ok gang!

1292
01:26:12,481 --> 01:26:13,582
Lets squill!

1293
01:26:24,300 --> 01:26:26,125
Mr.Curtiss, the fight's over.

1294
01:26:28,110 --> 01:26:29,677
Hey Boss!

1295
01:26:29,697 --> 01:26:31,264
Cmon hurry up!

1296
01:26:31,405 --> 01:26:32,432
I'm trying to be classy!

1297
01:26:32,452 --> 01:26:33,479
You idiot!

1298
01:26:35,534 --> 01:26:37,727
You a great seaplane engineer.

1299
01:26:37,747 --> 01:26:39,940
Keep it up Ms.Fio.

