01:26:40,070 --> 01:26:41,287
Bye!

1301
01:26:41,540 --> 01:26:42,960
Thank you.

1302
01:26:42,980 --> 01:26:44,400
And keep up the bathing!

1303
01:26:45,210 --> 01:26:46,567
And I want to say thanks to you too, Mr.

1304
01:26:46,587 --> 01:26:47,944
Curtiss!

1305
01:26:48,078 --> 01:26:51,298
Next time I'll propose you formally and skip the bet.

1306
01:26:51,925 --> 01:26:53,264
Ok.

1307
01:26:53,284 --> 01:26:54,623
But I already know my answer.

1308
01:26:55,303 --> 01:26:56,455
Fio!

1309
01:26:56,475 --> 01:26:57,627
You're going with Gina.

1310
01:26:57,754 --> 01:26:59,301
No!

1311
01:26:59,499 --> 01:27:01,201
I'm going with you.

1312
01:27:01,221 --> 01:27:02,923
You said we are in on this together.

1313
01:27:04,636 --> 01:27:08,266
Gina, take her to her respectable society please.

1314
01:27:10,444 --> 01:27:11,698
You always do this, Marco.

1315
01:27:11,718 --> 01:27:12,972
It's just not fair.

1316
01:27:15,574 --> 01:27:16,851
Sorry.

1317
01:27:16,871 --> 01:27:18,148
Off you go.

1318
01:27:23,447 --> 01:27:24,448
Let's go.

1319
01:27:56,521 --> 01:27:58,694
Here come the Italian Air Force.

1320
01:27:58,992 --> 01:28:00,662
I'm gonna draw them from the others.

1321
01:28:00,682 --> 01:28:02,352
You wanna help?

1322
01:28:03,705 --> 01:28:04,624
Sure.

1323
01:28:04,644 --> 01:28:05,563
Your face!

1324
01:28:06,333 --> 01:28:06,772
Hey wait up!

1325
01:28:06,792 --> 01:28:07,231
Turn around!

1326
01:28:07,251 --> 01:28:07,690
Get away from me!

1327
01:28:09,026 --> 01:28:25,886
Cmon, let me see Porco flew rings around Italian Air force and they never caught up with him again.

1328
01:28:26,510 --> 01:28:29,059
I stayed with Gina for a while and we became good friends.

1329
01:28:32,195 --> 01:28:34,650
But soon I decided, it was time to go back to Milan.

1330
01:28:36,250 --> 01:28:39,113
Through the years there have been a few wars and a...

1331
01:28:39,223 --> 01:28:42,213
good deal of turmoil, but my friendship with Gina has remained strong.

1332
01:28:45,013 --> 01:28:48,113
I am now President of the Piccolo Co., and we are busy designing all sorts of...

1333
01:28:48,313 --> 01:28:55,112
radical new planes but I take time out every summer to visit the Hotel  Adriana.

1334
01:28:55,247 --> 01:29:00,094
